I guess you're talking about {{Cli#run}} instead of {{main()}}? Please see the v0 patch.

Another point is that, should we use ToolRunner to call the {{Cli#run()}} instead of calling it directly? In that way, the ToolRunner can provided some features like setting {{CallerContext}}, accepting [Generic_Options|https://hadoop.apache.org/docs/r2.7.2/hadoop-project-dist/hadoop-common/CommandsManual.html#Generic_Options] (do we plan to support that) in LogLevel?
